        <remarks>
          <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] provides a default client certificate validator that verifies the client certificate against the trusted people store and also checks that the certificate chains up to a valid root. A custom validator can be implemented to obtain a different behavior. This property allows a custom validator to be specified.  
  
 ]]></format>
